name: ABR Electric
tag_list: electrician, troubleshooting, wiring-problems, recessed-lighting, doorbells, tripping-breakers, panel-replacement
overview:
ABR Electric provides electrical repair and upgrade services to local homeowners.

We work one-on-one with homeowners to identify and correct safety and National Electrical Code Violations.

Frequently, we will upgrade interior/exterior lighting, add circuits for new appliances or equipment (big screen TVs, spas, dishwashers, Sub Zero refrigerators, etc.).

Our goal is to do the work right, make a positive memory for the customer and have fun.
